<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Interesting America CMS</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="512x512" href="{{ '/images/uploads/favicon-512.png' | url }}?v=20260526-favicon-01">
    <style>
      :root{color-scheme:light}
      *{box-sizing:border-box}
      body{margin:0;font-family:Inter,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",sans-serif;background:#f4f7fb;color:#0b1020}
      main{max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;padding:64px 24px}
      .panel{display:grid;gap:20px;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(11,16,32,.08);border-radius:24px;background:#fff;box-shadow:0 24px 54px rgba(15,23,42,.08)}
      h1{margin:0;font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,56px);line-height:.96;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.05em}
      p,li{margin:0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;color:#475569}
      ul{margin:0;padding-left:1.2em;display:grid;gap:8px}
      code{padding:.18em .42em;border-radius:8px;background:#f3f4f6;color:#0b1020}
      .actions{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px}
      .button{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:48px;padding:0 18px;border-radius:999px;background:#0b1020;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;font-weight:600}
      .button--secondary{background:#eef2f7;color:#0b1020}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <div class="panel">
        <h1>CMS Admin</h1>
        <p>This staging website is hosted on GitHub Pages. Payload CMS is a server application and is not served from this static `/admin/` URL.</p>
        <p>For local staging, use:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><code>npm run cms:bootstrap</code> once</li>
          <li><code>npm run cms:dev</code> for the CMS on <code>http://127.0.0.1:3000/admin</code></li>
          <li><code>npm start</code> for the frontend on <code>http://127.0.0.1:8080</code></li>
        </ul>
        <p>A public CMS staging URL requires a separate server deployment target for the `cms/` app. GitHub Pages alone cannot run Payload.</p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="button" href="{{ '/' | url }}">Back to Website</a>
          <a class="button button--secondary" href="http://127.0.0.1:3000/admin">Open Local Admin</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
